00:10:08.260 --> 00:10:10.260
Dan setiap gen memberikan sidik jari.

00:10:10.260 --> 00:10:15.260
Harap diingat bahwa kami menguji 25.000 gen di dalam genom

00:10:15.260 --> 00:10:19.260
